; form-static-analyzer-band.fk - witness compile-time Form lint/static analysis.
;
; Verdict 16383 when every claim lands:
;   1     valid attributed expression is allowed for execute/JIT
;   2     unbound symbol is caught
;   4     arity mismatch is caught
;   8     literal div by zero is caught
;   16    literal mod by zero is caught
;   32    literal list nth out-of-bounds is caught
;   64    head/tail over statically empty list is caught
;   128   missing source attribution is caught
;   256   unsafe expression is blocked before execute
;   512   unsafe expression is blocked before JIT lowering
;   1024  defn param shadowing a known fn is flagged exactly once (code 207)
;   2048  renamed (healed) param raises no shadow flag
;   4096  the shadow flag is a WARN — it does not block execute
;   8192  the body's call through the shadowing param is a bound indirect
;         call, not an unbound-callee error (locals shadow globals)
;
; Run:
;   ./fkwu --src observe/tests/form-static-analyzer-band.fk
;
; preludes: observe/form-static-analyzer.fk

(do (form-static-analyzer-check))
